Package: ZemmourLib
Title: A Collection of Custom R Functions from Zemmour Lab
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Zemmour", email = "zemmour@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides a set of custom R functions primarily designed for
    analyzing single-cell RNA-seq and CITEseq data, especially useful with Seurat
    objects. It includes utilities for plotting, UMAP visualization, differential expression
    analysis with limma-trend, and other data processing tasks.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
